Record Player
  Has Name as String
  Has Score as Int

Make Pair be Tuple with 7 and 8
Make First and Second be Pair
Say "tuple total {First plus Second}"

Make Scores be Map with "Ada" meaning 10 and "Grace" meaning 12
Make Ada and Grace be Scores
Say "map total {Ada plus Grace}"

Make Player be New Player with Name be "Linus" and Score be 271
Make Name and Score be Player
Say "{Name} scored {Score}"

Make Labels be Set with "beta" and "alpha"
Make Alpha and Beta be Labels
Say "{Alpha} then {Beta}"
